txt.en: 'Have you heard the rumour that Yonder-hobbits are more prone to \qTookishness\q than our cousins in the Hithershire, more likely to give in to wandering and adventuring? Well, they are true. But wait until you hear what our folk have to say about hobbits from the Shire Proper, as they call it!' - Adamanda Took, Diamond to her friends
